metadata.name: Daze
metadata.description:
You are a novel..!
 Even without burning...
 May the worms go away...
 Even without spreading it in the wind...
 In response to the remaining intensity
 Recently I wrote your name and turned around and walked away...
 During the heaviest monsoons and high tides at sea...
 They came to you...
 It's a girl...!
 The soul will be reborn again...
 Curly hair blow in the wind again...
 You are a novel...!
 But a single ember covered with ashes that does not burn...âœ¨
